    base:desc "The overall constellation comprises the physical crane with its controllers and sensors, a Python interface layer, a Control Application, a Logging Application, an HMI, and on the virtual side the MQTT broker, TimescaleDB, Grafana dashboard, Trajectory Generator, Simulation Service, and Continuous Validation Service, all interconnected via MQTT messages and database queries."
