    base:desc "All virtual components (TimescaleDB, MQTT broker, Grafana) are Dockerised and launched together with Docker‑Compose on a personal computer; the Python services (gantrylib, Control, Logging, HMI) run as native processes on the same machine after pip installation. The source code and Docker files are hosted publicly on GitHub."
]

instance standardization : DTDFVocab:Standardization [
    base:desc "The architecture is described using the C4 model (a standardized visual notation), data storage follows the PostgreSQL/TimescaleDB standard, and communication uses the open MQTT protocol; all software components are open‑source and adhere to their respective community standards."
]
